data_processing: Expression values were calculated by RMA algorithm using the affy package of Bioconductor (http://www.bioconductor.org/).
description: Lymphoid cells (FS-low, SS-low) from zebrafish kidney were subdivided into the SP and MP population (referred to as "zSP" and "zMP") based on the Hoechst fluorescence intensity.
extract_protocol_ch1: Cells were sorted into lysis buffer directly, and total RNAs were extracted using Absolutely RNA Nanoprep Kit (Stratagene) according to manufacturer's instructions.
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 microg of cRNA was hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Zebrafish Genome Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA was generated by 2 round of in vitro transcription (IVT) using MessageAmp II aRNA Amplification Kit (Applyied Biosystems).
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 3000.
